### Positive test: User can add a deposit with 0,01 amount
POST http://localhost:4111/api/v1/accounts/deposit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic a2F0ZTE5OTg6S2F0ZTE5OThA

{
  "id": 1,
  "balance": 0.01
}

### Positive test: User can add a deposit with positive value less than 5000 (4999.99)
POST http://localhost:4111/api/v1/accounts/deposit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic a2F0ZTE5OTg6S2F0ZTE5OThA

{
  "id": 1,
  "balance": 4999.99
}

### Positive test: User can add a deposit 5000
POST http://localhost:4111/api/v1/accounts/deposit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic a2F0ZTE5OTg6S2F0ZTE5OThA

{
  "id": 1,
  "balance": 5000
}

