### Positive test: User can update name with valid value - 2 words separated by space
PUT http://localhost:4111/api/v1/customer/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic a2F0ZTE5OTg6S2F0ZTE5OThA

{
  "name": "John Smith"
}

